      "text": "EFFECTIVE_START_DATE (Hire Date)  |  ORIGINAL_START_DATE  |  SENIORITY_DATE  |  PASS_PROBATION_DATE  |  RETIREMENT_DATE\nCURRENT_BUSINESS_UNIT_EFFECTIVE_DATE  |  CURRENT_JOB_EFFECTIVE_DATE  |  CURRENT_POSITION_EFFECTIVE_DATE\nCURRENT_JG_EFFECTIVE_DATE  |  CURRENT_PG_EFFECTIVE_DATE  |  CURRENT_CORPORATE_TITLE_EFFECTIVE_DATE  |  CURRENT_STORE_BRANCH_EFFECTIVE_DATE\nCURRENT_YEARS_IN_BUSINESS_UNIT  |  CURRENT_YEARS_IN_STORE_BRANCH  |  CURRENT_YEARS_IN_JOB\nCURRENT_YEARS_IN_POSITION  |  CURRENT_YEARS_IN_JG  |  CURRENT_YEARS_IN_PG  |  CURRENT_YEARS_IN_CORPORATE_TITLE\nYEAR_OF_SERVICE  |  EMPLOYEE_AGE_YMD\n→ Total: 19 date/year fields ที่เกี่ยวข้องกับ seniority logic",
